{"item_id": "df94771dc6:15", "source": "PxrPhasorNoise"}
{"item_id": "df94771dc6:16", "source": "Manifolds"}
{"item_id": "df94771dc6:17", "source": "Manifolds tell the renderer how to apply patterns on a surface. This controls features like repetition, placement, and size."}
{"item_id": "df94771dc6:18", "source": "PxrManifold2D"}
