{"item_id": "df94771dc6:78", "source": "Guidance for Writing Your Own Patterns"}
{"item_id": "df94771dc6:79", "source": "You do not need to be limited to the patterns that RenderMan provides.  If you follow the guidance in"}
{"item_id": "df94771dc6:80", "source": "OSL Patterns"}
{"item_id": "df94771dc6:81", "source": "you can build your own patterns.  XPU only runs OSL patterns, while RIS runs both C++ and OSL patterns."}
